title: Caesar Salad
instructions: Toss romaine lettuce with Caesar dressing, parmesan cheese, and croutons.

title: Greek Salad
instructions: Mix cucumber, tomatoes, red onion, feta cheese, and olives with olive oil.

title: Caprese Salad
instructions: Layer fresh mozzarella, tomatoes, and basil; drizzle with balsamic glaze.

title: Cobb Salad
instructions: Combine lettuce, chicken, bacon, avocado, blue cheese, and hard-boiled eggs.

title: Quinoa Salad
instructions: Mix cooked quinoa with cucumber, tomatoes, lemon juice, and herbs.

title: Fruit Salad
instructions: Mix assorted fruits and chill before serving.

title: Asian Sesame Salad
instructions: Toss cabbage, carrots, and edamame with sesame dressing.

title: Spinach & Strawberry Salad
instructions: Combine spinach, strawberries, walnuts, and balsamic dressing.

title: Avocado Chickpea Salad
instructions: Mash avocado with chickpeas, lemon juice, and herbs.

title: Broccoli Crunch Salad
instructions: Mix raw broccoli, sunflower seeds, cranberries, and creamy dressing.

title: Kale Caesar Salad
instructions: Massage kale leaves with Caesar dressing and top with croutons.

title: Lentil Salad
instructions: Mix cooked lentils with red onion, parsley, and olive oil.

title: Watermelon Feta Salad
instructions: Toss watermelon cubes with feta, mint, and lime juice.

title: Taco Salad
instructions: Layer lettuce, seasoned beef, cheese, tomatoes, and tortilla chips.

title: Pasta Salad
instructions: Mix cooked pasta with mayo, bell peppers, and sweet corn.

title: Asian Noodle Salad
instructions: Toss noodles with soy sauce, sesame oil, and vegetables.

title: Coleslaw
instructions: Shred cabbage and carrots, mix with mayonnaise dressing.

title: Beetroot Salad
instructions: Roast beets and mix with goat cheese, arugula, and walnuts.

title: Avocado Corn Salad
instructions: Combine avocado, corn, cherry tomatoes, and lime dressing.

title: Asian Cucumber Salad
instructions: Toss sliced cucumbers with rice vinegar, soy sauce, and sesame seeds.
